metadata.name: Urban Saints Genesis
metadata.description:
Urban Saints has been a part of my life for over 10 years.

Urban Saints was the first piece of personal artistic expression that I ever pursued in my life.  

Urban Saints is the reason I am still doing what I do today and I am fortunate to be able to do it for a living.

Urban Saints has helped me to be touched by countless incredible people.

Urban Saints has taught me to cherish each and every existing, new and future connection. 

Urban Saints has helped me visit places, that I wouldn't have been able to visit otherwise. 

Urban Saints has taught me to see beauty in everything.

Urban Saints has reminded me to never take anything for granted.

Urban Saints has made me appreciate life that much more in general.

I am not minting photos.

I am immortalising a significant part of myself.

As a person, as a professional, and as an artist.

Thank you!
